 # Annotated 12 lead ECG dataset

Contain 827 ECG tracings from different patients, annotated by several cardiologists, residents and medical students. It is used as test set on the paper: &quot;Automatic diagnosis of the 12-lead ECG using a deep neural network&quot;. https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-15432-4.

It contain annotations about 6 different ECGs abnormalities:
- 1st degree AV block (1dAVb);
- right bundle branch block (RBBB);
- left bundle branch block (LBBB);
- sinus bradyca
